title: Dominique Fils Aimé performs "Moi je t’aime" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Dominique Fils-Aimé performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded September 22, 2025.

Songs:
Feeling Like A Plant 00:19
Fall And All 04:32
Old Love 06:43
Moi je t’aime 11:15
There Is Probably Fire 14:50
Or Let It Burn 17:31
Our Roots Run Deep 18:22

Dominique Fils-Aimé - Vocal
Harvey Bien-Aimée - Drums

Étienne Miousse - Guitar

Host: Larry Mizell, Jr.
Audio Engineer: Julian Martlew
Guest Audio Engineer & Mixer: Simon Lévesque
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz
